        <updateDate>2022-01-31T17:24:25Z</updateDate>
        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><b>Kids Internet Design and Safety Act or the KIDS Act</b><br> <br> This bill prohibits operators of commercial online platforms that are directed to children from engaging in certain practices, including implementing features that encourage additional engagement with the platform, promoting certain types of content, and using certain advertising methods.</p>]]>
        </text>
      </summary>
